| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5357 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 93e5b8aa-97b8-5b73-8ae0-ae02ad0e4978"
